  "detailed_description": "<i>Running on Empty</i> is a minimal yet deep post-apocalyptic role-playing game with resource management mechanics (in 64x64 retro pixel graphics!)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880960/extras/287a22ea283ef3d7b968c247532cd9bf.poster.avif?t=1726511784\" width=200 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880960/extras/287a22ea283ef3d7b968c247532cd9bf.webm?t=1726511784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880960/extras/287a22ea283ef3d7b968c247532cd9bf.mp4?t=1726511784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your sole mission is to retrieve the package from the place far away.<br>Go through the cruel world.<br>Run between settlements, help residents, deal with raiders to complete the mission.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880960/extras/dd227b9baba6a92895e893a136dc12c7.poster.avif?t=1726511784\" width=200 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880960/extras/dd227b9baba6a92895e893a136dc12c7.webm?t=1726511784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880960/extras/dd227b9baba6a92895e893a136dc12c7.mp4?t=1726511784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Managing your resources to survive in the wasteland<br></li><li>Multiple ways to finish the story<br></li><li>Leveling up your skills with skill points<br></li><li>Randomly generated maps<br></li><li>3 Factions to support or oppose<br></li><li>Steam achievements<br></li><li>Gunfights, sniping enemies, picking locks, hacking terminals...</li></ul><br><strong>It is highly recommended to read the game manual before playing.<br>(It's available on the side bar at the right part of the store page and the library page)</strong>",
